This is the README for the Tripwire_driver

This is a cloud connected device which when activate fires a laser beam across and and detects when the beam is broken. It connects to the ninja cloud so is easily integrated with your other home security and automation devices.

Features:
• Single powered unit - The laser and sensor are in the same device, so only one unit needs to be powered

• Set up mode to assist you with aligning the tripwire the first time

• Programable

